name: generator-yosapy
description: AngularJS test generator. It's an yeoman generator. Generates customized Jasmine test for your angularJs file, You will be amazed to see most of these autogenerated custom test cases are actually passing and it took your code coverage for that file from 0% to 40%-50% without writing a single line of code, ain't that freaking awesome!!!
author: Saptarshi Chatterjee <saptarshichatterjee1@gmail.com>
